modName: Todd Howard ASMR Menu Music Replacement - DELETED
summary: Replaces the Menu Music with Todd Howard ASMR
descriptionHtml:
Replaces the Menu Music with Todd Howard ASMR[b] (I was asked to port it to Skyrim.)

[/b]How to install[b] - [/b]Unzip the Zip file with WinRar (Or any program that extracts files.) place the extracted Music file into the Data folder, if it ask to replace
anything click yes. I also suggest backing-up the original menu music before replacing it.
